org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.process.traversal.util

Interface Metrics

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ImmutableMetrics, MutableMetrics

    public interface Metrics
    Holds metrics data; typically for .profile()-step analysis. Metrics may be nested. Nesting enables the ability to capture explicit metrics for multiple distinct operations. Annotations are used to store miscellaneous notes that might be useful to a developer when examining results, such as index coverage for Steps in a Traversal.
    Author:
    Bob Briody (http://bobbriody.com)
